highlights.text: “One Of My Life” by BLVCKHEART and K6Y has been on Viral Songs Thailand the longest, at 233 days straight.
YUNGTARR has the most spots on Viral Songs Thailand. “Satin” is the highest at #24.
“คนที่โชคดีกว่า” by OABNITHI is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Thailand, up 11 spots at #66.
“Confess Your Love” by Jiandro and ola.wav is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Thailand at #28.
